    <text>
        <body>       
                <pb n="1"/>
            <p>313W30<lb/>
                15&#47;1&#47;86<lb/></p>
            <p>Rev S Morais<lb/>
                My dear Sir<lb/></p>
            <p>I am sorry duty will<lb/> detain you next week.<lb/></p>
            <p>I saw Dr Kohut yesterday<lb/> going to his house&#8212;he wished to call to<lb/> see me but as I was on the East side that<lb/> morning&#44; next to the same Avenue by which<lb/> he lives&#44; I thought it better for me to save him<lb/> the trouble.<lb/></p>
            <p>He is as you know in favor of our<lb/> movement&#59; his ideas however  are very
                big&#8212;he<lb/> spoke of &#36;100000 to start with&#8212;but of course<lb/> I told him we will not begin on a big scale&#45;<lb/> Details must be left to after Consideration&#59;<lb/> He could  not easily see you Sunday anyhow. He<lb/> has school in morning and wedding in<lb/> aft&#39;noon.<lb/></p>
            <p>If you can <hi rend="underline">without trouble</hi><lb/> get away Monday or Tuesday or Wednesday&#44; or<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="2"/>
                
            <p>Thursday&#8212;any day&#45;&#45; I will be at<lb/> your Services.<lb/></p>
            <p>If Monday or Thursday&#44; you had better go<lb/> to Mr. Piza&#39;s first in the morning as I can<lb/> meet you at his house more easily&#44; for I<lb/> work at the Laboratory on the East Side from 9 a m.<lb/> to 11 or little after&#44; and can get to Mr. P&#39;s in<lb/> 15 or 20 minutes.<lb/></p>
            <p>In any case write to Mr. Piza saying when you<lb/> will be there&#44; so that he can remain home. I<lb/> saw him last night at his house&#44; and told him<lb/> I would so write you. He is&#44; he says&#44; always very<lb/> busy when at the office.<lb/></p>
            <p>I think too&#44; it would be better if&#44; when you decide<lb/> what day you will come&#44; you write Rev Dr Drachman<lb/> 22 Newark Avenue&#44; Newark&#44; N.J. &#40;or 22 Newark<lb/>Avenue&#44; <hi rend="underline">New Jersey</hi>&#63;&#41; to meet you in New York&#44; either<lb/> at Mr. Piza&#39;s&#44; or here.<lb/></p>
            <p>You know it takes time to get round in New York&#59;<lb/> Dr. Kohut lives farther East than Mr Piza&#59; my<lb/> brother lives far west.<lb/></p>
            <p>Your best plan is  to see Mr Piza first&#44; then<lb/> Dr. Kohut&#44; then my brother&#59;  maybe you had better<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="3"/>
            <p>drop a card also to my brother when you decide what day<lb/> you will come&#44; for he goes out of town once a week and will<lb/> make his arrangements accordingly.<lb/></p>
            <p>If you give me <hi rend="underline">timely</hi> notice&#44; I will save you all trouble of<lb/> writing and will write Mr Piza&#44; Dr Drachman&#44; Dr Kohut and<lb/> my brother stating you will call such and such a morning<lb/> or aft&#39;noon.<lb/></p>
            <p>Wishing you&#91;&#63;&#93; Shabat<lb/>
                &#91;&#63;&#93; H Pereira Mendes<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="4"/>
            <p>I hope however  that your coming next week will not prevent<lb/> your coming a week or so after to meet my father and Mr de<lb/>Sola&#59; The resolution our trustees adopted was that we should all meet<lb/> and formulate some plan to be submitted for action to them and others of the<lb/>laity who must supply the cash.<lb/></p>
            <p>Mr. Piza last night deprecated fear of failure and thought we invited it by<lb/> working too quickly.<lb/></p>
            </body>
